    A >> pal >> tott >> t1 >> t2 >> t3 >> t4 >> t5 >> t6 >> t7 >> t8;

    B >> pal2 >> totp >> p1 >> p2 >> p3 >> p4 >> p5 >> p6 >> p7 >> p8;

